partnerDetails.about: RG Jack and Son is a family-run wholesaler, providing a huge range of high quality electrical and lighting products. Our stock includes brand names like C.B.I, Crabtree, Schneider, Osram and Legrand, to name a few. And with an ever-expanding range to suit domestic and industrial applications, you’re sure to find everything you need under one roof.
